352
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:07,239
What does it mean?

353
00:14:07,239 --> 00:14:07,599
I don't get it.

354
00:14:07,599 --> 00:14:08,440
Everyone,

355
00:14:08,719 --> 00:14:09,919
