368
00:14:40,479 --> 00:14:41,159
Come on, someone!

369
00:14:41,159 --> 00:14:42,119
Let go of me!

370
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:44,359
Help!

371
00:14:45,479 --> 00:14:47,479
