374
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,919
Untie me quickly!

375
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,239
You scoundrel.

376
00:14:53,239 --> 00:14:54,479
Let me see who you are.

377
00:14:57,479 --> 00:14:58,679
Yu Changya?

378
00:14:59,119 --> 00:15:00,320
How come it's you?

379
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:03,479
