383
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:11,280
Come.

384
00:15:13,119 --> 00:15:14,080
Do you get it?

385
00:15:14,799 --> 00:15:15,640
Yes.

386
00:15:16,119 --> 00:15:17,080
Is it nice?

387
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:19,440
